  [ Marcin Sulikowski ]
  * buildpackage-funcs: Fix whitespace handling in .dsc paths.  MR: !4

  [ Hideki Yamane ]
  * createbuildenv:
    + Use packages from APTCACHE during debootstrap.  Closes: #432088; MR: !6
