pbuilder (0.169) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Loic Minier ]
  * List amd64 in pbuilder-uml's Architectures; thanks Mattia Dongili.

  [ Junichi Uekawa ]
  * pdebuild-internal now runs hooks A, B, C, and D. (closes: #342613)
